{\large \textbf{\begin{tcolorbox}\textsc{Key Projects}\end{tcolorbox}}}
\begin{itemize}
\item \textbf{Snowball: Co-founded Start up at E-cell IIT Kanpur} 
\begin{itemize}
\item Successfully pitched Snowball, a fund raising platform for non profits, at a startup bootcamp organized by Wadhwani Foundation, hosted by E cell IITK, securing a spot amongst the top startups. Conducted extensive market research and surveyed 15 decision makers of Non Profits all over India, and around 10 potential users to create an MVP and a pitch deck that included customer persona and competition analysis.
\item Gathered user feedback and recognized the product's shortcomings, leading to a strategic pivot. Demonstrated strong problem-solving skills by adapting to new insights and pivoting the product to better fit the market demand.
\item Built a data-driven approach and a user-focused mindset to product development by conducting market research, surveys and building an MVP, which ultimately led to a better understanding of user needs and preferences. Showcased strong leadership skills by working collaboratively with a team of two to execute on this product vision.
\end{itemize}
\item \textbf{CTO-Ninja: Freelance Business Associate}\hfill\hfill(\textit{May'17-Ongoing})
\begin{itemize}
\item Successfully utilized LinkedIn Sales Navigator strategies and attended industry meetups to expand my professional network and engage with prospects from diverse regions, resulting in increased lead generation and revenue opportunities for CTO-Ninja.
\item Utilized Beautiful Soup to gather sponsored websites on Google, employed an email finder tool to obtain email addresses for each website, and utilized Mailchimp to send audit reports of website performance to businesses as a means of solicitation and landed prospects.
\item Implemented strategies to improve the company’s website ranking on Google by optimizing the website for user-friendliness and mobile-friendliness. Conducted extensive keyword research utilizing Ahref, Google Analytics, and Google Search Console to identify high-performing keywords and incorporated them into the website's content.
\item Employed Lead Forensics to identify anonymous website visitors and converted them into potential clients, resulting in a significant increase in the company's sales pipeline.
\end{itemize}
\item \textbf{Terasology: Open source — Contributor}
\begin{itemize}
\item An open source sandbox game similar to minecraft, that runs primarily
on Java.
\item Contributed using Github, by collaborating with a multi-national team of
core contributors to implement various types of gameplay settings in a
voxel world
\item Enhanced the gameplay experience by implementing health loss on
entering hazards, rewards on quest completion, time synchronization on all
players in a multiplayer game, changes in physical capabilities according to
change in height of character
\end{itemize}
\item \textbf{Self Project: Reputation System} \hfill\hfill(\textit{May'17- July'17})\\%\textbf{Mentor: }\textbf{Prof. Manindra Agrawal}, Department of Computer and Science Engineering.
\vspace{-4mm}
\begin{itemize}
\item Developed a reputation system for Web3 companies to identify fraudulent Ethereum transactions. Utilized Infura APIs to gather transaction data and applied the Isolation Forest algorithm to detect anomalies and flag potentially fraudulent transactions.  
 
\end{itemize}
